Miscellaneous Highlights: The Golden State Warriors defeated the New Orleans Pelicans 104-89 at Chase Center on October 31, 2024.
The Warriors improved to 4-1 on the season, while the Pelicans fell to 2-3.
The attendance at Chase Center was 18,064.
Others: Golden State Warriors: Draymond Green (14 points, 5 rebounds, 6 assists), Moses Moody (14 points, 3 rebounds, 6 assists), Andrew Wiggins (13 points, 2 rebounds, 7 assists); New Orleans Pelicans: Zion Williamson (12 points, 6 rebounds, 4 assists), Brandon Ingram (14 points, 5 rebounds, 6 assists), CJ McCollum (16 points, 3 rebounds, 2 assists).
